Comment: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She swayed palely and then disappeared.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like a hazy steam...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:23.06,LowerLeft,NTP,0,0,0,,The Yuragi Inn's Yuuna
Comment: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I made it! Yukemuri hot springs town.
Comment: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is where my new life begins!
Comment: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You saw a woman with a completely smooth face\Nwithout eyes or a nose?
Comment: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You folks are pulling my leg!
Comment: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's true! We saw it!
Comment: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was the face...
Comment: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,something like this?
Comment: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't threaten the elderly!
Comment: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Comment: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Comment: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The name's Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a hands-on psychic.
Comment: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was a classical, mischievous monster\Ncalled a mujina.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You were a big help.
Comment: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}How can we thank you?
Comment: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, don't worry about it.
Comment: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you know Yuragi Inn?
Comment: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a boarding house\Nthat used to be a hot springs inn.
Comment: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The rent is only 1,000 yen a month!
Comment: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Plus breakfast and lunch, 15,000 yen!
Comment: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scenic Open-Air Hot Spring
Comment: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And you can use the hot spring all you want!
Comment: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sure, the rent is cheap, but that place...
Comment: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's haunted, right?
Comment: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When Yuragi Inn was still a traditional inn,\Na student's corpse was found in the open-air bath.
Comment: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That spirit is still there.
Comment: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you know the rumor, then why...
Comment: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One good punch and that ghost\Nwill be running for the hills.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No more rivers or waterfalls!
Comment: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My first hot bath in a month!
Comment: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A ghost, huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder what the dude's like.
Comment: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, no matter how terrifying of a demon it is,\NI'll clobber it with my tempered fists.
Comment: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's here, huh?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ghost...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...of Yuragi Inn!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The temperature is perfect.
Comment: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's floating.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What, what, what is it?
Comment: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's definitely the ghost!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Comment: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can it be that...
Comment: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...you can actually see me?
Comment: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't see! I can't see you, so hide!
Comment: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no!
Comment: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh shoot.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you can see me, can't you?
Comment: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry! I just couldn't...
Comment: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only have one method of exorcism.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you all right?!
Comment: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Punch them hard and drive them away.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hang in there! Please hang in there!
Comment: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But a woman...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't punch a woman.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh?
Comment: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Comment: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Comment: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right. I was in the outdoor bath...
Comment: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're Fuyuzora Kogarashi, right?
Comment: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Comment: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have the honor\Nof being the innkeeper for Yuragi Inn.
Comment: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My name is Chitose Nakai.
Comment: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the innkeeper?
Comment: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! I take care of all the residents\Nof Yuragi Inn.
Comment: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're finally up!
Comment: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, how about a drink\Nso we can get to know each other?
Comment: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geez, minors can't drink.
Comment: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such a stickler.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.62,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm Nonko Arahabaki. What's your name?
Comment: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kogarashi, huh?
Comment: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's a pleasure to meet you.
Comment: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's showing, geez!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You said your name is Fuyuzora Kogarashi?
Comment: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you do anything\Nthat disrupts the moral tenor of Yuragi Inn,
Comment: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I, Sagiri Ameno,\Nwill inflict punishment on you.
Comment: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're too harsh, Sagi.
Comment: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That goes for you too, Nonko!
Comment: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A man is right there,\Nso please wear more proper clothing!
Comment: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the...
Comment: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where were you burrowing?!
Comment: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya likes warm places.
Comment: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd heal it for you.
Comment: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since this place is haunted,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard only eccentric people live here, but...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your room number, Kogarashi?
Comment: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's room number 4.
Comment: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Number 4?
Comment: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. Number 4, eh?
Comment: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, it was nice knowing you.
Comment: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shoot. That's too bad.
Comment: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Comment: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sheesh. What's with them?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yeah, I forgot to ask about the ghost.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Room 204
Comment: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can they live here without a problem\Nwhen they know the inn is haunted?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it doesn't bother them\Nbecause they have zero spirit sense?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is my room from today!
Comment: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's such a luxury\Nwhen I can sleep on tatami mats!
Comment: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A butt's sticking out of the wall?
Comment: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Comment: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come out, ghost girl!
Comment: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can touch me?
Comment: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, sto—
Comment: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!\NI didn't want to scare you, so I was hiding!
Comment: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That wasn't hiding!
Comment: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, just come out!
Comment: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Comment: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I haven't introduced myself yet, have I?
Comment: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me start over.
Comment: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Yuuna Yunohana,\Na ghost bound to Yuragi Inn.
Comment: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a surprise!
Comment: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you're a psychic, Kogarashi?
Comment: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, more or less.
Comment: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um... Then I'd like to check something.
Comment: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do I look like to you?
Comment: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look like? A high school girl in a yukata.
Comment: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really can see me properly, huh?
Comment: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Apparently normal people can only see me\Nas a white shadow.
Comment: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then when we were in the outside bath too,\Nyou saw everything...
Comment: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm kind of happy,\Nbut also kind of embarrassed!
Comment: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm at a loss.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not only a girl,\Nbut doesn't seem to be a bad ghost.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I can only do an exorcism by punching.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never really learned difficult techniques\Nlike "barriers" or "forced ascension."{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-Um, I have no intention\Nof cursing you or tormenting you.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm just a friendly bound ghost.
Comment: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the more reason I can't punch her.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's already this late?
Comment: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll put the futons out.
Comment: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, there!
Comment: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm a ghost,\Nbut I can touch anything when I want to.
Comment: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been a ghost for a long time now.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You intend to sleep here?
Comment: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since I'm a bound spirit,\Nthis is the only room where I can sleep.
Comment: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Comment: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the two of us\Nare going to live in the same room?
Comment: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um... I guess\Nthat's what it boils down to, in the end.
Comment: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh shoot.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm suddenly getting self-conscious.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, would I be a nuisance?
Comment: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not especially. I don't mind.
Comment: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?! That's a relief!
Comment: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I an idiot?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how cute she is, she's a ghost!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, goodnight!
Comment: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't sleep.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, are you awake?
Comment: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, why did you come to Yuragi Inn?
Comment: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ever since I was born, I've been susceptible\Nto getting possessed by spirits.
Comment: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That kept causing problems\Nfor everyone around me,
Comment: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I kept getting handed off\Nto the next guardian.
Comment: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end, I was possessed by a day trader.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That resulted in a major financial loss,\Ndebt hell, and homelessness.
Comment: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After that, I became an apprentice\Nto a medium.
Comment: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The idea was that by defeating evil spirits,\NI could get back my normal life.
Comment: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That must have been tough.
Comment: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No matter where I went,\NI was treated as a burden.
Comment: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure that's what I was.
Comment: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you came here, Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because you aren't afraid of me at all.
Comment: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've been able\Nto talk with someone like this in this room.
Comment: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I'm happy.
Comment: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your lingering regret?
Comment: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lingering regret?
Comment: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My mentor told me that the longer a spirit\Nsticks around, the more likely it would turn evil.
Comment: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So it would be better if your lingering regret\Nwas resolved so you can ascend before it's too late.
Comment: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi...
Comment: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you happen to be worried about me?
Comment: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, not especially...
Comment: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...
Comment: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! When I get shaken up,\NI have a habit of causing poltergeist activity.
Comment: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ow...
Comment: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry! Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yukemuri Grill
Comment: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you next week!
Comment: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right! Now I've got a part-time job\Nand a place to live!
Comment: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukemuri Town, huh?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a nice place.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to send the ghost packing right away,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have to do something about it.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm happy that you came here, Kogarashi.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she becomes an evil spirit,\Nthen she'll definitely go to Hell.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can I do?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could I have thrown him in the river?
Comment: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kogarashi is mad at me.
Comment: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, what's your lingering regret?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's the only person who's asked me that.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi! Welcome h...
Comment: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Comment: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this? Who are you?
Comment: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am Sekkan Tsujishouten,\Na Gouma monk of the Gudon Clan.
Comment: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gudon? Sorry, could you repeat that?
Comment: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pitiful spirit that lingers in this world.
Comment: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will use my skills to ascend you to Heaven!
Comment: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have a bad feeling about something.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're just a little girl!\NDon't you want to go to Heaven?
Comment: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My ascension technique\Nspecializes in "forced ascension."
Comment: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Leave this world\Nbefore you become an evil spirit.
Comment: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go to the Land of Perfect Bliss.\NBecome reincarnated.
Comment: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can choose the path you desire!
Comment: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forced ascension!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she'll eventually become an evil spirit,\Nthen maybe this is...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't... want to...
Comment: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I still want to stay in this world.
Comment: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are still many things\NI want to see and do!
Comment: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, I have a new friend!
Comment: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to learn more about Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're just a dead person.
Comment: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I'll use all of my strength to ascend you!
Comment: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My barrier...
Comment: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Boy, are you a medium, too?
Comment: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then why are you interfering?
Comment: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is mine and her room.
Comment: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't break into somebody's room!
Comment: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the living, there is nothing more immoral\Nthan siding with the dead!
Comment: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The living, the dead, it doesn't matter!
Comment: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I decide who I get to punch!
Comment: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems like\Nyou don't want to ascend to Heaven.
Comment: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But then, eventually you'll go to Hell.
Comment: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know that I need to\Nascend at some point, but...
Comment: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. Okay, then I'll help you.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll help you resolve\Nyour lingering regret, Yuuna.
Comment: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you become happy!
Comment: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hey, why are you crying?
Comment: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No one has said that to me ever in my life!
Comment: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, besides, I doubt there are any other rooms\Nthat go for 1,000 yen a month.
Comment: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that you're dirt-poor, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please stay dirt-poor forever!
Comment: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I flat-out refuse!
Comment: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me do something, too!
Comment: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're ever in trouble, just tell me!
Comment: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, stay back!
Comment: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Comment: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please don't touch me!
Comment: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Again?!
Comment: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scenic Open-Air Hot Spring
Comment: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's kind of noisy, isn't it?
Comment: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe something's happened\Nto Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, huh?
Comment: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We finally get a boy,
Comment: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but being in Yuuna's room,\Nit's only a matter of time.
Comment: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you never know.
Comment: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was really horrible.
Comment: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought I told you.
Comment: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you do anything\Nthat disrupts the moral tenor here,
Comment: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will inflict punishment on you.
Comment: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, you've got the wrong idea, everyone!
Comment: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is, um, my fault.
Comment: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi touched my chest, and then...
Comment: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't on purpose—
Comment: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No excuses!
Comment: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Take that!
Comment: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that's when Kogarashi thought, "Maybe\NI should've let her been exorcised after all."{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, all my faults aside,
Comment: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward\Nto us living together.
Comment: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time: Yuuna and the Hot Spring Ping Pong
Comment: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't miss the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:39.99,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Cô ấy lượn lờ trên không trung rồi biến mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:45.21,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,cứ như làn hơi nước mờ ảo vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:59.00,YamiSora,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&\3c&H408DE1&\3a&HFF&}............... {\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H408DE1&\3a&H00&}YAMISORA FANSUB\NBiên dịch: Tuyền Oa Minh Nhân
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:23.63,Episode,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Cô nàng Yuuna ở nhà trọ Yuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.56,Default - Top,NTP,0,0,0,,Đến rồi! Thị trấn suối nước nóng Yukemuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây sẽ là nơi cuộc sống mới của mình bắt đầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hai người thấy một người phụ nữ không mắt không mũi, mặt thì láng bóng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quý khách thích nói đùa ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật đấy! Bọn tôi thấy thật mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khuôn mặt ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,trông như thế này phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có doạ mấy ông bà già chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cháu là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cháu là Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Một linh lực giả dùng thể pháp ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.78,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}Ở đây Fuyuzora nói đến yêu quái không mặt (貉 - Mujina) của tác giả Lafcadio Hearn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vừa rồi là Mujina, loài yêu quái hay chọc phá người khác rất cổ điển.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 bác không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,May mà có cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải cảm tạ cháu thế nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thôi không cần đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2 bác biết nhà trọ Yuragi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khu nhà trọ ấy hồi trước từng là lữ quán suối nước nóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giá trọ chỉ 1000 yên 1 tháng thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tính cả bữa sáng với bữa trưa thì khoảng 15 nghìn yên!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngoài ra còn được thoải mái tắm suối nước nóng nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À thì, tiền trọ tuy thấp nhưng chỗ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bị ma ám phải không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khi còn là lữ quán, người ta đã tìm thấy xác một nữ sinh trong bồn tắm lộ thiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồn ma ấy giờ vẫn còn lảng vảng ở đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu đã nghe lời đồn rồi thì sao cháu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dăm ba con vong cháu đấm cho phát là thăng thiên ngay ấy mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không phải tắm sông hay thác nước nữa rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lần đầu tiên được tắm nước nóng trong suốt một tháng!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ma à...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết mặt mũi nó ra sao nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà dù có là thứ ma quỷ đáng sợ cỡ nào, thì ăn một đấm của mình cũng thăng thiên hết thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.16,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Ở ngay đây luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.46,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồn ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.80,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,ở nhà trọ Yuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vừa đủ nóng luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.19,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Lơ lửng?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế gì thế?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.77,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Không thể sai được, cô ta là ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,cậu có thể thấy mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không thấy! Không thấy gì hết! Nên mau che lạ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,B-Biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.33,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Bỏ mẹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết ngay cậu thấy được mình mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, mình lỡ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.39,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình chỉ có duy nhất một cách trừ yêu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.43,Default - Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cậu không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.35,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,là đấm vỡ mồm chúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:55.81,Default - Top,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gắng lên, gắng lên...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.39,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng nếu là phụ nữ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.77,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,thì éo thể đấm được...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em tỉnh rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chỗ này là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi, mình đang ở trong bồn tắm lộ thiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em là Fuyuzora Kogarashi-san nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao lại biết tên tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị đây vinh dự được làm bà chủ nhà trọ Yuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tên chị là Nakai Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nakai-san... là nhóc á?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng, chị là người chăm lo cho những khách trọ ở nhà trọ Yuragi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng cũng tới.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè nè, làm vài ly giao hữu nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt là, trẻ vị thành niên không được uống đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Khắt khe ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị là Arahabaki Nonko, còn em?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-chan à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hân hạnh được gặp nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.63,Default - Top,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì mà show hết ra thế?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngươi nói mình là Fuyuzora Kogarashi ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu nhà ngươi dám làm gì ảnh hướng đến nếp sống ở nhà trọ Yuragi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,thì chuẩn bị tinh thần nhận hình phạt của Ameno Sagiri này đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sigi-chan gắt thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Câu đó dành cho Nonko-san mới đúng đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đàn ông con trai đang ở đây đấy,\N chị ăn mặc đàng hoàng dùm cái.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em đào hang ở đâu vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya-san thích những nơi ấm cúng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tự nhiên làm cái gì vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lâu lâu Yaya mới chữa vết thương cho người khác vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.14,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nơi này nghe nói là bị ma ám...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.56,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn mình thì chỉ nghe nói ở đây toàn mấy người dị thường...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè nè, Kogarashi-san ở phòng số mấy thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phòng số 4 ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phòng số 4!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra vậy, ra là phòng số 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, rất vui khi được quen cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiếc thật đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya đi ngủ đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:28.71,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt là, họ bị gì thế không biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.89,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,À mà mình quên hỏi vụ hồn ma mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.10,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết nơi này bị ám mà sao họ sống thản nhiên nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.39,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hay là vì họ cảm nhận được nó nên không bị chọc phá?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.06,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Hay là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ nay đây là phòng mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Được ngủ trên thảm tatami, đúng là sang quá mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có cái mông lòi ra từ bức tường?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra khỏi đó mau, ma nữ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao cậu lại chạm được vào người mình?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, dừng lại—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, vì không muốn làm cậu sợ nên mình tính nấp đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nấp nấp cái búa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mau ra đây đi đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình vẫn chưa tự giới thiệu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, bắt đầu lại nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình là hồn ma chôn chân ở nhà trọ Yuragi, tên Yunohana Yuuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngạc nhiên thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san là linh lực giả phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À thì, có thể nói là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, cho mình xác nhận một chuyện nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu thấy bề ngoài của mình trông như thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế nào à? Thì một nữ sinh cấp 3 mặc yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy là bạn thấy được mình thật phải không?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bình thường ai cũng thấy mình là một cái bóng trắng cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rồi tới khi mình ra tắm ở bồn tắm lộ thiên, thì bị cậu thấy hết...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm xúc vui mừng với xấu hổ nó lẫn lộn vào nhau hết rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.88,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Trớ trêu thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:40.43,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhỏ này vừa là con gái, vừa không có chút gì giống kẻ xấu cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:44.31,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn mình thì chỉ có thể trừ ma bằng nắm đấm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:50.48,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mấy phép khó nhai như kết giới hay cưỡng chế siêu thoát \Ntrước giờ mình có học qua đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, mình không có ý định nguyền rủa hay hành hạ cậu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình chỉ là hồn ma bị chôn chân thân thiện thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.74,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Càng có thêm lý do không thể đấm nhỏ rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã muộn thế này rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình đi trải nệm nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, thế là thế nào hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuy mình là ma, nhưng mình có thể chạm vào bất cứ gì tuỳ thích đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồn ma lão làng mà lị!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Định ngủ ở đây luôn à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình là hồn ma bị chôn chân mà, nên chỉ có thể ngủ ở phòng này thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hai đứa mình... sẽ ở chung một phòng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ờ thì, rốt cuộc thì, đúng là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.83,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Bỏ mợ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.29,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Tự nhiên mình thấy rối quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình có phiền quá không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không sao, tớ không để bụng đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật à?! Thế thì tốt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.63,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình bị ngáo à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:06.47,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù có đáng yêu cỡ nào thì nhỏ ấy cũng là ma mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, chúc cậu ngủ ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.53,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngủ éo được...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san, cậu còn thức không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, vì sao Kogarashi-san lại chuyển đến nhà trọ Yuragi thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ khi chào đời, tớ rất dễ bị ma ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Năng lực đó gây rất nhiều phiền phức cho những người xung quanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ thì bị chuyển từ người này nuôi sang tay người khác nuôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng, tớ đã bị hồn ma của một thương nhân tài chính ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế là cảnh nợ nần chồng chất, tổn thất tài chính, rồi mất hết nhà cửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế nên, tớ đã nhận một linh lực giả làm sư phụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Với suy nghĩ có thể dùng cách trừ ma diệt quỷ để phục nguyên lại cuộc sống bình thường của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hẳn phải gian nan lắm nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đi đến đâu cũng bị coi là cái của nợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà, lúc nhỏ tớ đã như vậy rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình rất vui, vì Kogarashi-san đã đến đây với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì Kogarashi-san không hề sợ mình mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là lần đầu tiên mình được nói chuyện với người khác trong căn phòng này,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là, mình vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, điều mà cậu tiếc nuối là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nuối tiếc ấy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sư phụ nói rằng, làm ma càng lâu, thì càng dễ hoá thành ác linh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là, tốt hơn nên giải quyết điều mà cậu nuối tiếc để siêu thoát trước khi quá muộn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không lẽ, cậu lo cho mình sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cũng không hẳn đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G-Gì thế...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:39.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Poltergeist là những hiện tượng do ma quỷ gây ra, thường là dịch chuyển đồ vật
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, mình có tật xấu\Nkhi bị hoảng thì sẽ kích hoạt poltergeist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi! Cậu không sao chứ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật ạ?! Cảm ơn chú nhiều lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, từ tuần sau mong chú giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngon! Giờ mình đã có chỗ ở lẫn chỗ làm thêm rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.27,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thị trấn Yukemuri à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.44,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nơi này được đấy chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.15,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình thì chỉ muốn mau chóng giải quyết vụ ma quỷ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.28,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,nhưng chẳng biết phải làm sao nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:56.70,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình rất vui, vì Kogarashi-san đã đến đây với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.46,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu nhỏ ấy hoá thành ác linh, thì nhất định sẽ bị đày xuống địa ngục.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.22,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình có thể làm được gì đây?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tự nhiên bị mình đẩy xuống sông như thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết Kogarashi-san có giận mình không nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:29.15,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, điều mà cậu nuối tiếc là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trước giờ chỉ có mỗi Kogarashi-san hỏi mình chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san, mừng cậu v...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chết thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì thế này?! Ông là ai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bần tăng là hàng ma pháp tăng thuộc tộc Gudon, \NTsujishouten no Sekkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gudon? Xin lỗi nhưng ông nhắc lại được kh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hỡi yêu linh đáng thương nán lại nơi trần thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thuật chú của bần tăng sẽ đưa ngươi về cõi cực lạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.65,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình có linh cảm xấu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiểu cô nương như cô mà không muốn về cõi cực lạc sao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Thiên thăng trận" của bổn tăng là thuật cưỡng chế siêu thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hãy rời khỏi trần thế trước khi hoá thành ác linh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hãy về với chốn cực lạc, để được luân hồn chuyển kiếp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cô có thể chọn con đường mà mình muốn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.26,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Cưỡng chế siêu thoát!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.85,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu cuối cùng nhỏ ấy hoá thành ác linh, thì cứ thế này sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tôi... không muốn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tôi vẫn còn muốn nán lại thế giới này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vẫn còn nhiều thứ tôi muốn thấy, nhiều việc tôi muốn làm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hơn nữa, mãi tôi mới có được bạn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tôi muốn hiểu Kogarashi-san hơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bản thân thí chủ vốn là người đã khuất...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế thì bổn tăng sẽ dùng toàn lực siêu thoát cho thí chủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kết giới của ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tiểu tử, nhà ngươi cũng là linh lực giả à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế thì sao lại cản đường ta hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là phòng của tôi, và của cô ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có tự tiện xông vào phòng người khác!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Người của dương giới đứng về phía người của âm giới là trái với luân thường đạo lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Âm giới dương giới đây éo quan tâm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thằng nào ăn đấm là do ta quyết định!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra cậu không muốn về chốn cực lạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu vậy thì cậu sẽ bị đày xuống địa ngục,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình biết, đến một ngày nào đó, mình cần phải siêu thoát, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế à, vậy tớ sẽ giúp cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ sẽ giúp cậu giải quyết những vướng bận khi còn sống, Yuuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tớ sẽ đem đến hạnh phúc cho cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Này, sao lại khóc vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là lần đầu tiên trong đời có người nói vậy với mình đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà chắc không còn phòng trọ nào cho thuê 1000 yên 1 tháng nữa đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật tốt vì Kogarashi-san là kẻ nghèo rớt mồng tơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ giờ cậu hãy cứ nghèo như thế nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin từ chối thẳng thừng nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hãy để mình giúp cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu cậu gặp phải chuyện gì thì cứ nói với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, lùi lại mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, xin lỗi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có động vào mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lại nữa à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.56,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}SUỐI NƯỚC NÓNG LỘ THIÊN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì mà ồn thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không lẽ có chuyện xảy ra với tên Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-chan ấy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mãi mới có con trai tới trọ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,mà lại thuê trúng phòng của Yuuna-chan, thì chỉ còn vấn đề thời gian thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không không, chưa biết trước được gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là ác thật mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hình như ta nói với ngươi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu nhà ngươi dám làm gì ảnh hướng đến nếp sống ở nhà trọ Yuragi này...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,thì chuẩn bị tinh thần chịu phạt đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, mọi người, không phải thế đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là, à thì, là lỗi của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san đã sờ trúng ngực mình, rồi sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, không phải cố ý đâ—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn dám viện cớ hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đỡ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:50.56,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,"Đáng ra nên để nhỏ ấy thăng luôn cho rồi!"\NSuy nghĩ ấy chợt thoáng qua đầu Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi cậu, Kogarashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À thì, chuyện này do mình mà ra cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ nay mong mọi người giúp đỡ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Next Episode,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}CÔ NÀNG YUUNA VÀ BÓNG BÀN SUỐI NƯỚC NÓNG
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhớ đón xem tập tuần sau nhé.
